NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::BumpVersionFromGit - DEPRECATED -- use
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Git::NextVersion instead

VERSION
    version 0.009

SYNOPSIS
    In your F<dist.ini>:

         [BumpVersionFromGit]
         first_version = 0.001       ; this is the default
         version_regexp  = ^v(.+)$   ; this is the default

DESCRIPTION
    NOTE This distribution is deprecated. The module has been reborn as
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Git::NextVersion and included in the
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Git distribution.

SUPPORT
  Bugs / Feature Requests
    Please report any bugs or feature requests by email to
    "bug-dist-zilla-plugin-bumpversionfromgit at rt.cpan.org", or through
    the web interface at
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Bump
    VersionFromGit>. You will be automatically notified of any progress on
    the request by the system.

